{
  "stem": "20616.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we made some examples of the most blatant ones.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were tried and convicted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, we got supplements to [GERMAN] that people had filled up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I made a mistake.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Instead of joining the party in 1938, as I said, I actually joined in 1932.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I made a slight mistake.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Of course, some people were so conscientious they said, I actually joined in-- in the end of 1937 instead of the end of 1938 or I neglected to say that I was in a-- a chess club-- and I joined a chess club or some innocuous organization that they didn't mention on the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, you know, we had to differentiate between somebody joining in 1938 and 1932.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In fact, we found somebody who joined in 1922, when Hitler first was one of the first members of the Nazi party.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I found that out accidentally by a letter that we found that was signed by Himmler-- not Hitler, but Heinrich Himmler, one of his-- the head of the SS and of some [GERMAN], some old party members.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was a very respected person and they said, no, he was never a Nazi.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I couldn't-- I went to my assistant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He knew all the people in town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He says, he was an anti-Nazi if I ever saw one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, but how is that possible?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I'll call him into the office one-- one day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we started talking and I said, I have something here that disturbs me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Is that the time when you actually joined the Nazi party, in 1938 or whenever it was?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he said, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I said, weren't you a member of the Nazi party much earlier than that?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, he turned white.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
